name: Traffic Takedown
description:
Get behind the wheel and hold on tight, because you're in for the ride of your life! In "Traffic Takedown", your brakes have failed and you must navigate the busy highways while avoiding the expensive cars and hitting the rest. Use your skills and strategy to slow down and avoid total destruction. With fast-paced action and nail-biting challenges, "Traffic Takedown" is the ultimate test of your driving ability. So put the pedal to the metal and prepare to bring the chaos to the roads!

Made by Papieog and SpellArray
